# Environment
- Always assume a Windows development environment.
- Prefer PowerShell and Windows CLI tooling over bash.

# Tooling
- For API changes, first apply changes on PHP side, then run "npm run api" and use the generated TypeScript services in frontend.
- Do not manually change files in app/src/app/services/api as these are auto-generated!

# Error handling
- Whenever a non-normal API interaction occurs (for examle, 404 may be a valid business scenario. 400 or 500 are not), details must be logged in  error log

# Coding style
- Follow the existing TypeScript ESLint config.
- Do not introduce new frameworks or libraries without asking.

# Best practices
- ALWAYS begin your response by telling me what AI model you are using. Just say the name of the model like (claude-3.5-sonnet or gemini-2.5-pro)